Libadalang & Langkit
====================

This repository hosts both Langkit and Libadalang.

Langkit is a library whose purpose it to ease building engines for analyzing
programming languages.  Libadalang is one of these engines using Langkit.

You will find a README dedicated to Langkit in langkit/README and another one
dedicated to Libadalang in ada/README.

Common dependencies
===================

TL;DR
-----

$ pip install -r REQUIREMENTS.dev

To build the documentation
--------------------------

- Sphinx (pip install sphinx)
- Pygments (pip install pygments)

To build generate, build, test and use Langkit
----------------------------------------------

- The mako template system for Python (pip install mako)
- Measuring code coverage with coverage.py (pip install coverage)
